<%/* about.eta */%>
<div class="about-page">
  <h1>About Strabon</h1>
  <p>
    Strabon is a temporal atlas of archaeological sites and historical cities.
    It visualizes how settlements, cultures, and political entities evolved
    across 12,000 years of human history.
  </p>
  <p>
    Named after <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strabo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Strabo</a>
    (64 BC – 24 AD), the Greek geographer and historian.
  </p>
</div>
